left to float by♪

00:31:14.340 --> 00:31:19.820
♪Baby, changed? To me it's all the same♪

00:31:20.660 --> 00:31:22.380
♪There's a dreamscape
where I still call your name♪

00:31:22.380 --> 00:31:23.980
Today, I'm really honored

00:31:24.020 --> 00:31:26.660
to officiate the wedding
of Mr. Ji Baijian

00:31:26.660 --> 00:31:28.260
and Ms. Song Zhizhi.

00:31:28.460 --> 00:31:29.460
At this moment,

00:31:29.540 --> 00:31:31.020
I'd like to ask the groom.

00:31:31.500 --> 00:31:33.300
Are you nervous?

00:31:34.910 --> 00:31:37.980
♪Yet through the pain,
I'll never leave your side♪

00:31:37.980 --> 00:31:38.740
To be honest,

00:31:39.540 --> 00:31:40.140
I am.

00:31:40.660 --> 00:31:43.920
♪It feels just like an illusion♪

00:31:44.580 --> 00:31:48.340
♪Hold me tight.
Don't let go of this dream♪

00:31:48.340 --> 00:31:48.820
Here.

00:31:52.740 --> 00:31:53.660
The ceremony is about to start.

00:31:53.740 --> 00:31:54.700
I'll head out.

00:31:54.780 --> 00:31:56.060
There will be a cue sound later.

00:31:56.100 --> 00:31:57.660
Just follow the procedure and come out.

00:31:58.920 --> 00:32:01.920
♪When I fall♪

00:32:02.190 --> 00:32:05.600
♪Please catch me♪

00:32:06.720 --> 00:32:11.160
♪Don't say you'll understand♪

00:32:12.180 --> 00:32:12.820
Come in.

00:32:43.580 --> 00:32:48.300
♪From this moment on, I no longer care♪

00:32:49.580 --> 00:32:51.900
♪No more noise in my ears♪

00:32:52.940 --> 00:32:56.300
♪That's the peace
I've always yearned for♪

00:32:56.940 --> 00:32:59.060
♪Who was I trying to change for?♪

00:32:59.060 --> 00:33:02.540
♪Smiling, crying, complaining♪

00:33:03.140 --> 00:33:10.100
♪That's the contentment
I should learn to embrace♪

00:33:10.220 --> 00:33:13.700
♪Honestly, I don't care♪

00:33:13.700 --> 00:33:17.460
♪How many times you've hurt me♪

00:33:17.460 --> 00:33:21.020
♪What you call sincere devotion♪

00:33:21.060 --> 00:33:24.580
♪Maybe I've just grown numb♪

00:33:24.660 --> 00:33:28.100
♪Honestly, I don't care♪

00:33:28.180 --> 00:33:31.500
♪Even if I've strayed♪

00:33:31.700 --> 00:33:35.220
♪I'm still crying for someone♪

00:33:35.500 --> 00:33:42.380
♪Crying over losing to my own pride♪